1.desc: A café with tastes from around the world: coffee from the Royal Navy, bread from the Northern Parliament, and pizza from Sardegna.
1.name: Manjuu Café

2.desc: Piping-hot soup dumplings, bursting with authentic Dragon Empery flavors. Step right up and get a basket!
2.name: Dumpling House

3.desc: The trifecta of happiness: a tasty hamburger, ice-cold cola, and crispy fries.
3.name: Burger Joint

4.desc: These commemorative dangos from the Sakura Empire almost look too beautiful to eat.
4.name: Dango Shop

5.desc: My friend asked me to pick something up! S-seriously, I'm not into this kind of literature...
5.name: Manjuu Bookstore

6.desc: Wow, what a spectacular array of games they have this month... This ghost's wallet isn't going to survive...
6.name: Manjuju Game Shop

7.desc: No longer shall the gacha gods deny me!!!
7.name: Manjuu Capsule Shop

9.desc: It's a need for speed, not a need for angular velocity! Arrrrgh...!
9.name: Dizzy Manjuu

10.desc: Manjuus may be flightless, but roller coasters have given them a taste of their true potential.
10.name: Cloud-Chasing Manjuu

11.desc: I fear no heights. But gachas? Those scare me...
11.name: Xtreme Bunjuu

12.desc: C'mon, you should know by now that this game is all about the booty.
12.name: Manjuu Pirate Ship
